---
title: Honey-Soy Pumpkin & Garlic Rice Bowl with Ginger Greens & Japanese Mayo
description: If you're a long time lover of the honey and soy combo, wait till you try it on roasted pumpkin! Sounds unusual, we know, but teamed with aromatic ginger veggies and a delectable Japanese mayo, you're in for a real treat.

*Unfortunately, this week's broccolini was in short supply, so we've replaced it with broccoli. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-honey-soy-pumpkin-garlic-rice-bowl-67db48ee.jpg
